descriptions.see_description: In the input, you should see...large areas with one significant colored pattern different than its background.
descriptions.grid_description: The output grid size...same size as the significant pattern.
descriptions.do_description: To make the output, you have to...copy the significant pattern.

descriptions.see_description: In the input, you should see... a grid with many shapes in it including one which is the biggest and is a different color
descriptions.grid_description: The output grid size... is the size of the height and width of the biggest colored shape.
descriptions.do_description: To make the output, you have to... copy only the biggest shape into the output grid

descriptions.see_description: In the input, you should see...a dense color block inside the big back ground
descriptions.grid_description: The output grid size...is the size of the small dense part
descriptions.do_description: To make the output, you have to...copy the small dense part
